{"tid":91834,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊巴謙莫域：請珍惜朗尼","createTime":"2017-01-23T06:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T09:02:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6781d922c5d1bb5ed5e2a1e2d5a1cae45c47c20","tid":91834,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/76/82/wayne-rooney-premier-league-stoke-v-man-utd_d1vax0jdzann1fiuvs8l3z7ft.jpg?t=-1040608726&amp;w=620&amp;h=430\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2F76%2F82%2Fwayne-rooney-premier-league-stoke-v-man-utd_d1vax0jdzann1fiuvs8l3z7ft.jpg%3Ft%3D-1040608726%26w%3D620%26h%3D430&h=678bb627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域認為英倫球壇沒有真正重視過朗尼，希望外界對於這位球星多一點尊重。<br />\n<br />\n朗尼攻入靚絕罰球幫助紅魔鬼逼和史篤城，射入250球之後成為曼聯史上入球最多的球星。<br />\n<br />\n同時，朗尼代表英格蘭射入過53球，也是打破了前人卜比查爾頓入球紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n不過，伊巴謙莫域認為英倫球壇沒有好好重視朗尼這位球星。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域說：「他是全能球員，離開球場也是隊友之間的領導人。他幫助隊友發揮出最佳水準，他知道何時入球，何時助攻，永遠都是勤力及戰意一流。」<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域指，英倫球壇未有真正重視朗尼的價值：「人人都知道朗尼是誰，但這個國家沒有好好珍惜他。今時今日還有沒有這種質素的前鋒？給我一些名字吧。看看曼聯歷史上有這麼多好球星，他的入球紀錄在這些球星之上，這是難得的成就，可以和他做隊友令我感到自豪。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=do1kgsn4wvWs8BeP3lr9iAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=210883dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"56030aff0e0e6eec4db951493cde8107b6d6dfd8","tid":91834,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:34:59.000Z","msg":"迷西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8171706b58df1b942aef1186e9f671932f5e66","tid":91834,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"反西又輸"},{"pid":"1f2d5a5944aa84d6726d1c750dbd20f0e1eb9d40","tid":91834,"uid":19599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"永續朗隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696fda9253fe2cfb0827b7715ae3fd7a1305e7e8","tid":91834,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T06:36:15.000Z","msg":"朗尼：請珍惜伊巴謙莫域"},{"pid":"ae1b88669f0370bdebf9a04336ec53b60552b6e9","tid":91834,"uid":2550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:07:13.000Z","msg":"衰在唔夠靚仔..."},{"pid":"b9d3d937dfe9574e910278410995fec892f4bd56","tid":91834,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"少左句 認真...."},{"pid":"2d12e5915fa0943ba1f488e64484db62dfa97b10","tid":91834,"uid":15211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:20:47.000Z","msg":"請珍惜朗尼, 你也會有人妒忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e140c4a6b0042b332e1c8b65514365e194bb0fc","tid":91834,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"有冇邊個一級球星冇公開迷西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c84117dd0c120d9a5466402b8d042e3ebca7ff6","tid":91834,"uid":53676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由上場起我開始迷朗隊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556accae68a5bed564e7575430e665394e154922","tid":91834,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:32:04.000Z","msg":"好有型"},{"pid":"61ee350d6b4ef3d6094832dddb267fa8388691ec","tid":91834,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"足協欠污泥一個世界盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}